# Flathub aktivieren
https://flathub.org/setup/Debian

# Best Tipps from Average Linux User for Debian 11:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=VGvbn9Bn-gI

## Some Bash Commands mentioned in the video above:
### Install Build Essentials 
sudo apt install build-essential dkms linux-headers-$(uname -r)

### Install ubuntu-restricted-extras
sudo apt install ttf-mscorefonts-installer rar unrar libavcodec-extra gstreamer1.0-libav gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly gstreamer1.0-vaapi

### Install Microsoft Fonts Compatibility
sudo apt install fonts-crosextra-carlito fonts-crosextra-caladea

### Decrease swappiness (important for ssd users)
cat /proc/sys/vm/swappiness # gives usually like 60 back.

nano /etc/sysctl.conf
#### add "vm.swappiness=10" at the end of the file
#### CTRL & O to save
#### CTRL & X to exit nano
#### reboot your system.

### Change Grub Boot Menu Waiting Time
sudo nano /etc/default/grub
#### Change "GRUB_TIMEOUT=5" to "GRUB_TIMEOUT=0"
#### CTRL & O to save
#### CTRL & X to exit nano
sudo update-grub

### Install UFW Firewall on Debian
sudo apt install ufw
sudo ufw enable
